data.description: Recently remodeled 4Br/2.5Ba gorgeous home in sought after Gwinnett County school district! The kitchen is open to the family room and features white cabinets, walk-in pantry, built in gas oven and a built in microwave oven, separate gas stove, granite countertops, kitchen island, beautiful laminate floors! The owner's suite is a must see! Oversized, trey ceilings, sitting area and beautiful bay windows. The recently remodeled owner's bathroom will impress you- tiled shower with frameless shower glass, white double vanity with granite countertops, tiled garden tub and a large walk in closet! Plenty of space and abundant daylight! Loft area on the second floor. Swim/Tennis community with a nature trail. Easy access to 316 and I85, Mall of Georgia, restaurants and entertainment.
